Misty, there are a number of threads here that can give you the information that you seek.  These comments sometimes have to be sifted through to get the gold.  But they are honest and real feelings that we vets deal with on a daily basis.  It is heartening to see others seeking vets out to find out what did occur.  How often in history has an event that changed a country's course does one get to talk to the participants in that event?  So ask away. 
